        <mxCell id="vxh4Z2YMwEft1CRg36e7-28" value="The appliance responds to all queries from the Internet and internal network by sending its responses to the DMZ interface (1.2.2.1) on the firewall.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The appliance only needs a single default route to the firewall. The firewall then routes the traffic where it needs to go." style="text;strokeColor=none;align=left;fillColor=none;html=1;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
